      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a functional, budget-friendly option for someone looking for a reliable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car shows noticeable signs of wear both inside and out, including some minor scratches on the exterior and visible aging of the interior upholstery. It has been maintained regularly in the past, but a buyer should expect that some minor repairs or part replacements may be necessary in the near future to keep it running optimally. Overall, it's a solid, honest car that reflects its age and usage.",
