    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive preservation. This exceptional vehicle presents in showroom-grade condition, having been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. From the flawless exterior finish to the untouched interior, every detail reflects a history of careful ownership and uncompromising care. For the driver who demands nothing less than perfection, this represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly exemplary specimen.",
      "price": 48900.0,
